title: CVS Health 's number of stores 2005 to 2018
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Number of stores. In total the number of data points it has is 14.
In general Number of stores has rose over the Year.
The most drastic increase took place within the Year 2014 and 2015.
Maximum Number of stores, about 9967.0 was reported at Year 2018
The lowest Number of stores, of value 5474.0 was reported at Year 2005
